Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.36,0:23:04.00,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fade(200,200)}若是伸出雙手或許就能傳達到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.43,0:23:01.88,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,說話也會更輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.75,0:23:07.58,Default 1,NTP,0,0,0,,我…會努力
